uqobo: Igama elivame kakhulu ukumela isenzakalo samanje sekilasi ngaphakathi kwendlela
njenge: Inikeza imojuli engenisiwe noma into isibizo
uhlu lokuqondisisa: I-Paradigm yokudala uhlu ngaphakathi komugqa owodwa
ukusika: Indlela yokukhipha izingxenye zeyunithi yezinhlamvu usebenzisa izinkomba
i-docstring: Iyunithi yezinhlamvu yamadokhumenti enamathiselwe kumsebenzi noma isigaba
indlela emile: Indlela engenakho ukufinyelela ekilasini noma kuzibaluli zesibonelo
indlela yekilasi: Indlela eyamukela ngokungagunci lelo klasi njengepharamitha yokuqala
indlela yesibonelo: Indlela eyamukela ngokungagunci isibonelo njengepharamitha yokuqala
numpy: Umtapo wezincwadi owaziwa kakhulu we-python ohlinzeka ngokuyinhloko izinga eliphezulu, imisebenzi yezibalo egxile kuhlu.
umqhubi we-walrus: Umsebenzisi ovumela ukuqaliswa kokuguquguquka ngaphakathi kwebhulokhi yesitatimende uma
konke: Igama lokuguquguquka komhlaba wonke kusetshenziswa kumaphakheji acacisa amamojula azovezwa ekungenisweni kwe-wildcard
args: Isiteketiso sinikezwe izimpikiswano ezingezona zegama elingukhiye
kwargs: Isiteketiso sinikezwe izimpikiswano zamagama angukhiye ngokunganaki
phambili slash: Isihlukanisi sezinhlamvu ukuze sidinge ama-agumenti kwesokunxele saso ukuze abe ama-positional agumenti
inkanyezi: Isihlukanisi sezinhlamvu sibe izimpikiswano zamagama angukhiye
